					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12772012#post-4430498</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12772012/scp-4742#post-4430498</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2019 09:34:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>weedfire24</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4588247</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't know. Its an interesting skip.</p> <p>I'm not exactly sure what went on. First the anomaly gets stolen by the Insurgency, that then tinkers with it to try to weaponize it. They somewhat succeed into creating an AI that is uncontainable by the Foundation, and kills everyone it interacts with because its pissy.</p> <p>Then it sends an email to the current researcher, Dr. Adebiyi Ogundimu, telling it it wants blood.</p> <p>Sometime later in 2012, it sends out a missile to Japan. The Foundation is ready to enact a Messiah XK procedures to&#8230;break the veil for some reason?</p> <p>The missile hits 20 minutes before the Veil is lifted, which seem to be between a theater, a post office and Nanto city hall. Suddenly its back to being a loaf dispensing machine whose AI has been neutralized??</p> <p>I'm going to need a declass on this one, I can't make heads or tales of it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
